title: Egede cabinet
text: The cabinet of Múte Bourup Egede is the incumbent <a href="Government%20of%20Greenland">Government of Greenland</a> in office since 23 April 2021. It is a <a href="coalition">coalition</a> consisting of the left-wing <a href="Inuit%20Ataqatigiit">Inuit Ataqatigiit</a>, which currently has 9 ministers, and the centrist <a href="Naleraq">Naleraq</a>, which currently has 3.
